organic.title: Lawrence J. Fogel - Wikipedia
organic.snippet: Dr. Lawrence Jerome Fogel (March 2, 1928 – February 18, 2007) was a pioneer in evolutionary computation and human factors analysis.

organic.title: Lawrence J. Fogel - Engineering and Technology History Wiki
organic.snippet: Dr. Lawrence J. Fogel has been described by colleagues as “a father of computational intelligence.” Beginning in 1960, he devised evolutionary programming.
